genresAdvancedInfo.name: hawaiian indie
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Hawaiian indie music is characterized by its laid-back, beachy vibe and often incorporates elements of folk, rock, and pop. The lyrics often reflect the natural beauty of Hawaii and its people, with themes of love, life, and the ocean.
